{"BR": {"BR_id": "1073", "BR_author": "darshats", "BRopenT": "2020-03-24T06:40:39Z", "BRcloseT": "2020-03-27T18:09:11Z", "BR_text": {"BRsummary": "[BUG] The formula to generate decayed rating in data_transform module has a bug?", "BRdescription": "\n <denchmark-h:h3>Description</denchmark-h>\n \n The formula for decay of rating appears incorrect:\n lambda x: x['Weight'] * math.exp(-math.log2((t_ref - pd.to_datetime(x['Timestamp'])).days / T))\n It should be:\n lambda x: x['Weight'] * math.exp(-((t_ref - pd.to_datetime(x['Timestamp'])).days / T)*math.log2)\n <denchmark-h:h3>In which platform does it happen?</denchmark-h>\n \n All platforms\n <denchmark-h:h3>How do we replicate the issue?</denchmark-h>\n \n <denchmark-h:h3>Expected behavior (i.e. solution)</denchmark-h>\n \n <denchmark-h:h3>Other Comments</denchmark-h>\n \n \t"}, "comments": {"comments_0": {"comment_id": 1, "comment_author": "darshats", "commentT": "2020-03-27T18:09:11Z", "comment_text": "\n \t\tClosed by <denchmark-link:https://github.com/microsoft/recommenders/pull/1074>#1074</denchmark-link>\n  thanks for raising the issue <denchmark-link:https://github.com/darshats>@darshats</denchmark-link>\n \n \t\t"}}}, "commit": {"commit_id": "dae37730c0ddbd66329227b8878c19b2ab956ab7", "commit_author": "Scott Graham", "commitT": "2020-03-27 14:07:33-04:00", "commit_complexity": {"commit_NLOC": "None", "commit_CCN": "None", "commit_Nprams": "None"}, "changed_files": {"file_0": {"file_change_type": "MODIFY", "file_Nmethod": 0, "file_old_name": "notebooks\\01_prepare_data\\data_transform.ipynb", "file_new_name": "notebooks\\01_prepare_data\\data_transform.ipynb", "file_complexity": {"file_NLOC": "None", "file_CCN": "None", "file_NToken": "None"}, "hunks": {"hunk_0": {"Ismethod": 0, "added_lines": "37,44,58,92,110,142,149,156,163,170,177,184,191,198,205,212,219,226,233,240,269,298,320,352,359,366,373,380,387,394,401,408,415,422,429,436,443,450,479,506,515,547,554,561,568,575,582,589,596,603,610,634,672,682,713,719